    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me\u2014perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years, so you can just hop in and go. I\u2019ve truly loved every mile in this beauty, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
