    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through its high-revving individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains robust with a recently serviced Double-VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points\u2014essential for long-term structural integrity. The chassis retains its signature balance with an M-tuned suspension and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery out of corners. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, this example shows honest pride of ownership with consistent maintenance intervals, making it a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for performance enthusiasts.",
